                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Key Achievements:</strong> Delivered comprehensive estimate within 2 weeks, identified $2.5M in cost savings through value engineering, and helped client secure project financing with detailed budget breakdown.</p>
                <p>This project demonstrates Benny Estimates' capability to handle large-scale residential developments with precision and efficiency, ensuring accurate budgeting and successful project execution.</p>`
            },
            2: {
                title: "Building Estimator Melbourne - Commercial Complex",
                content: `<p class="mb-4"><strong>Project:</strong> Commercial Office & Retail Complex, Melbourne</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Location:</strong> Melbourne CBD, Victoria, Australia</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Client:</strong> Melbourne Commercial Properties</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Project Scope:</strong> Complete cost estimation for a 15-story commercial building with ground-floor retail spaces, including structural frame, curtain wall systems, HVAC, electrical, plumbing, and interior fit-outs.</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Services Provided:</strong> Quantity takeoffs, subcontractor solicitation, material pricing, labor cost analysis, construction scheduling, and detailed bid package preparation.</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Key Achievements:</strong> Provided estimate within 10 business days, achieved 98% accuracy against actual construction costs, and helped client win project bid with competitive pricing.</p>
                <p>Benny Estimates delivered a comprehensive commercial estimating solution that met all client requirements and contributed to successful project execution.</p>`
            },
            3: {
                title: "Civil Construction - Infrastructure Development",
                content: `<p class="mb-4"><strong>Project:</strong> Road & Drainage Infrastructure, Regional NSW</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Location:</strong> Regional New South Wales, Australia</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Client:</strong> NSW Infrastructure Authority</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Project Scope:</strong> Civil estimating for 12km of roadway construction, including earthwork calculations, drainage systems, culverts, paving, and site restoration.</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Services Provided:</strong> Earthwork quantity calculations, cut/fill analysis, material specifications, equipment requirements, labor costing, and environmental compliance estimates.</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Key Achievements:</strong> Delivered detailed civil estimate meeting government requirements, helped secure project funding, and provided accurate material quantities preventing delays during construction.</p>
                <p>This infrastructure project showcases Benny Estimates' expertise in civil construction estimating and ability to handle complex, large-scale projects.</p>`
            },
            4: {
                title: "Home Renovations - Residential Construction",
                content: `<p class="mb-4"><strong>Project:</strong> Residential Home Renovation, Suburban Sydney</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Location:</strong> Sydney Suburbs, New South Wales, Australia</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Client:</strong> Private Homeowner</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Project Scope:</strong> Complete home renovation including structural modifications, kitchen remodeling, bathroom updates, new flooring, electrical upgrades, and landscaping.</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Services Provided:</strong> Material takeoffs, labor estimates, contractor quotes, permit cost analysis, and detailed project budget breakdown with contingency allowances.</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Key Achievements:</strong> Provided accurate renovation estimate that matched final construction costs within 3%, helped homeowner make informed decisions about material selections, and identified cost-saving alternatives.</p>
                <p>Benny Estimates provided comprehensive residential estimating services that enabled successful home renovation completion on time and within budget.</p>`
            },
            5: {
                title: "Bridge Construction - Infrastructure",
                content: `<p class="mb-4"><strong>Project:</strong> Bridge Construction Over River</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Location:</strong> Regional Australia</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Client:</strong> Transport Infrastructure Authority</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Project Scope:</strong> Complete estimating for a 300-meter bridge structure including foundations, piers, structural steel, concrete deck, and approach roadways.</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Services Provided:</strong> Structural steel takeoffs, concrete quantity calculations, foundation estimates, labor costing, equipment requirements, and comprehensive bid package preparation.</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Key Achievements:</strong> Delivered complex bridge estimate within project timeline, coordinated with engineering team for accurate specifications, and provided detailed breakdown supporting successful contractor selection.</p>
                <p>This bridge project demonstrates Benny Estimates' capability in specialized infrastructure estimating requiring detailed technical knowledge and precision.</p>`
            },
            6: {
                title: "Kitchen Interior Design & Construction",
                content: `<p class="mb-4"><strong>Project:</strong> Luxury Kitchen Renovation</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Location:</strong> Sydney, Australia</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Client:</strong> Private Residence</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Project Scope:</strong> Complete kitchen renovation including custom cabinetry, stone countertops, high-end appliances, lighting design, and specialty finishes.</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Services Provided:</strong> Detailed material takeoffs for cabinets, countertops, fixtures, and appliances. Labor estimates for demolition, installation, electrical, and plumbing work. Finishing material specifications.</p>
                <p class="mb-4"><strong>Key Achievements:</strong> Provided accurate estimate within 48 hours, identified optimal material selections balancing quality and cost, and delivered comprehensive budget breakdown for client approval.</p>
                <p>Benny Estimates provided specialized kitchen estimating services that helped create a beautiful, functional space within the client's budget.</p>`
            }
        };

        // Open modal function - defined globally
        window.openModal = function(projectId) {
            console.log('Opening modal for project:', projectId);
            const modalOverlay = document.getElementById('modalOverlay');
            const modalTitle = document.getElementById('modalTitle');
            const modalBody = document.getElementById('modalBody');
            
            const project = projectData[projectId];
            if (project) {
                modalTitle.textContent = project.title;
                modalBody.innerHTML = project.content;
                modalOverlay.classList.add('active');
                document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
            } else {
                console.error('Project not found:', projectId);
            }
        }

        // Close modal function
        window.closeModal = function() {
            const modalOverlay = document.getElementById('modalOverlay');
            modalOverlay.classList.remove('active');
            document.body.style.overflow = '';
        }

        // Close modal on outside click
        window.closeModalOnOutsideClick = function(event) {
            if (event.target === document.getElementById('modalOverlay')) {
                closeModal();
            }
        }

        // Close modal with Escape key
        document.addEventListener('keydown', function(event) {
            if (event.key === 'Escape') {
                closeModal();
            }
        });

        // Theme functionality - wait for DOM to be fully loaded
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            console.log('DOM fully loaded');
            
            const themeToggle = document.getElementById('themeToggle');
            const themeIcon = document.getElementById('themeIcon');
            const themeText = document.getElementById('themeText');
            
            // Check for saved theme preference or use default
            const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme');
            const prefersDark = window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches;
            const currentTheme = savedTheme || (prefersDark ? 'dark' : 'light');
            
            // Apply theme on page load
            if (currentTheme === 'dark') {
                document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
                if (themeIcon && themeText) updateThemeUI('dark', themeIcon, themeText);
            } else {
                document.documentElement.classList.remove('dark');
                if (themeIcon && themeText) updateThemeUI('light', themeIcon, themeText);
            }
            
            // Add event listener for theme toggle if exists
            if (themeToggle) {
                themeToggle.addEventListener('click', function() {
                    toggleTheme(themeIcon, themeText);
                });
            }
        });

        // Update theme UI elements
        function updateThemeUI(theme, themeIcon, themeText) {
            if (theme === 'dark') {
                themeIcon.className = 'ri-sun-line mr-2';
                themeText.textContent = 'Light';
            } else {
                themeIcon.className = 'ri-moon-line mr-2';
                themeText.textContent = 'Dark';
            }
        }
        
        // Toggle theme function
        function toggleTheme(themeIcon, themeText) {
            if (document.documentElement.classList.contains('dark')) {
                document.documentElement.classList.remove('dark');
                localStorage.setItem('theme', 'light');
                updateThemeUI('light', themeIcon, themeText);
            } else {
                document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
                localStorage.setItem('theme', 'dark');
                updateThemeUI('dark', themeIcon, themeText);
            }
        }

        // Listen for system theme changes
        window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').addEventListener('change', (e) => {
            const themeIcon = document.getElementById('themeIcon');
            const themeText = document.getElementById('themeText');
            if (!localStorage.getItem('theme')) {
                if (e.matches) {
                    document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
                    if (themeIcon && themeText) updateThemeUI('dark', themeIcon, themeText);
                } else {
                    document.documentElement.classList.remove('dark');
                    if (themeIcon && themeText) updateThemeUI('light', themeIcon, themeText);
                }
            }
        });

        console.log('Our Projects Page Loaded');
        console.log('Script loaded successfully');
    </script>
</body>
</html>